WEBVTT

00:05:29.206 --> 00:05:31.389
We need to forgive fairly.

00:05:32.928 --> 00:05:37.398
Contrast the treatment globally
of child soldiers

00:05:37.422 --> 00:05:41.422
with the treatment of juvenile
offenders in the United States.

00:05:42.072 --> 00:05:45.644
International human rights
condemn and punish adults

00:05:45.668 --> 00:05:48.369
who involve children in armed conflict

00:05:48.393 --> 00:05:50.419
as those most responsible,

00:05:50.443 --> 00:05:54.053
but treat the children themselves
quite differently.

00:05:54.640 --> 00:05:56.702
The International Criminal Court,

00:05:56.726 --> 00:06:00.113
now with 122 member nations,